    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aio</ex></expan> Avi</supplied>dio Nigrino <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ato</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> pro <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>aetore</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost">decreta ex tabellis recitata XV</supplied> <expan><abbr>K</abbr><ex>alendas</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Octobr</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan>. cum rerum iudicatarum auctoritas cu<supplied reason="lost">stodienda semper sit<certainty locus="name" match="preceding-sibling::text()" cert="low"/>, servari<certainty locus="name" match="preceding-sibling::text()" cert="low"/> opor</supplied><lb break="no" n="3"/><supplied reason="lost">tet Cassii Longini decr</supplied>etum quod inter Delphos et Ambrossios in controversia quam INIM<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="4"/><supplied reason="lost">ediderit<certainty locus="name" match="preceding-sibling::text()" cert="low"/>, in qua<certainty locus="name" match="preceding-sibling::text()" cert="low"/> iis<certainty locus="name" match="preceding-sibling::text()" cert="low"/> fini</supplied>torem dederit Valerium Iustum, factamque ab eo deter<supplied reason="lost">minationem phinium.</supplied> <lb n="5"/><supplied reason="lost">nam ex epistula eiu</supplied>s apparuit ad Delphos publice scripta neque Ambr<supplied reason="lost">ossios neque Delphos deter</supplied><lb break="no" n="6"/>mina<supplied reason="lost">tionem</supplied><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> postea per aliquod iam annos. de Longini constitu<supplied reason="lost">tis, in controversia inter</supplied> <lb n="7"/>Delp<supplied reason="lost">hos et Ambros</supplied>sios de phinibus, determinatione per Valerium Iust<supplied reason="lost">um facta stari placet.</supplied> <lb n="8"/>in co<supplied reason="lost">nsilio adfue</supplied>runt <expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uintus</ex></expan> Eppius <expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>avius</ex></expan> Arrianus, <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Papius Habitus <expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> Liv<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>. </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> ἐκ τῶ<supplied reason="lost">ν πινά</supplied>κων μετειλλημμέναι πρὸ ιεʹ <supplied reason="lost">καλ(ανδῶν) Ὀκτωβρ(ίων)?. τοῦ ἐμμένειν τοῖς<certainty locus="name" match="preceding-sibling::text()" cert="low"/> κεκριμένο</supplied>ις <lb n="2"/>ὄντ<supplied reason="lost" cert="low">ος καὶ</supplied> λυσιτελεστάτου κα<supplied reason="lost">ὶ ἀναγκαιοτάτου<certainty locus="name" match="preceding-sibling::text()" cert="low"/>, ἀξία<certainty locus="name" match="preceding-sibling::text()" cert="low"/> ἐστὶ<certainty locus="name" match="preceding-sibling::text()" cert="low"/> φυλάτ</supplied>τεσθαι ἡ <lb n="3"/>Κασσί<supplied reason="lost">ου Λογ</supplied>γίνου το<supplied reason="lost">ῦ <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> κρίσις<certainty locus="name" match="preceding-sibling::text()" cert="low"/> ἣν κέκρικε<certainty locus="name" match="preceding-sibling::text()" cert="low"/> μεταξὺ Δελφῶ</supplied>ν καὶ Ἀμβροσ<supplied reason="lost">σί</supplied><lb break="no" n="4"/>ων, ἐν <supplied reason="lost">τῇ ἀμφισβητήσει <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>, ἐν ᾗ<certainty locus="name" match="preceding-sibling::text()" cert="low"/> ὁριστ</supplied>ὴν Οὐαλέριον Ἰο<supplied reason="lost">ῦσ</supplied><lb break="no" n="5"/><supplied reason="lost">τον αὐτοῖς ἔδωκε, καὶ ἡ ὁροθεσία ἡ τούτου. δῆλον γὰρ<certainty locus="name" match="preceding-sibling::text()" cert="low"/> ἡμῖν ἐγένετο ἐ</supplied>κ τῆς ἐπιστολῆ<supplied reason="lost">ς</supplied> <lb n="6"/><supplied reason="lost">αὐτοῦ τῆς πρὸς τοὺς Δελφοὺς μήτε Ἀμβροσσίους μήτε Δελφοὺς τὴν ὁρ</supplied>οθεσίαν <supplied reason="lost">τὴν</supplied> Ἰούστο<supplied reason="lost">υ</supplied> <lb n="7"/><supplied reason="lost"><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> ἔνια ἤδη ἔτη. ἐξ οὖν τῶν Λογγίνου καθεστώτων, ἐν τῇ</supplied> μεταξὺ Δελφῶν καὶ Ἀμβροσ<lb break="no" n="8"/><supplied reason="lost">σίων περὶ τῶν ὅρων ἀμφισβητήσει, τῇ ὁροθεσίᾳ τῇ Ἰούστου ἐμμένειν ἀρέσκε</supplied>ι. ἐν συμβουλίῳ ἐγένοντο <lb n="9"/><supplied reason="lost">Κόιντος Ἔππιος, Φλαούιος Ἀρριανός, Γάιος Πάπιος Ἅβιτος, Τίτος Λιβ<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></supplied>.
            </ab></div></div>
